OL,4,COcado to allow staff to work remotely
OL,5,Cfrom abroad
OL,6, Online grocer Ocado has told staff they
OL,7, can work remotely outside the UK for
OL,8, one month a year.
OL,10,FThe move comes as firms rethink
OL,11,Fworkplace policies after the pandemic.
OL,13,FThe firm's chief people officer, Claire
OL,14,FAinscough, told the Times newspaper
OL,15,Fthat its employees were still being
OL,16,Fencouraged to return to the office.
OL,18,FBusiness Secretary Kwasi Kwarteng told
OL,19,Fthe BBC that flexible working was "here
OL,20,Fto stay", but he would be urging his
OL,21,Fteam to come in more.
